  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964000/extras/896677d8b534eb9ba01cec763ee9e5e1.poster.avif?t=1772359152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964000/extras/896677d8b534eb9ba01cec763ee9e5e1.webm?t=1772359152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964000/extras/896677d8b534eb9ba01cec763ee9e5e1.mp4?t=1772359152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i>Are you actually reading this?</i></strong><br><br><i>Disclaimer: No human feelings were harmed during the making of this game</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>ABOUT THE ACTUAL GAME</i></h2><br>Escape a chaotic alien planet by fighting through hordes of frenzied monsters - Just kidding, it's a high school game where you play as Mochi, the gossip monger who can't keep her mouth shut. Step into the mind of Mochi and help her focus on her studies. It's your responsibility to control her urge to share every tantalizing piece of gossip to her fellow schoolmates.<br><br><i>\"Gossip is the only thing that spreads faster than wildfire in a dry forest.\" - Our in-house Psychologist</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>WHAT ARE YOU SUPPOSED TO DO?</i></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>As a High school student, all you have to do is focus on your studies.<br></li><li>Attend your daily classes.<br></li><li>Run some errands.<br></li><li>Finish the day without spilling a word, especially to the person the gossip is about.<br></li><li>Things can easily go out of hands if you share it even with a single person.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964000/extras/4cf1cfe0174f4605b10722c89b52c90b.poster.avif?t=1772359152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964000/extras/4cf1cfe0174f4605b10722c89b52c90b.webm?t=1772359152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964000/extras/4cf1cfe0174f4605b10722c89b52c90b.mp4?t=1772359152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>HOW DO YOU PLAY THE GAME?</i></h2><br>All you need is WASD functioning at their best on your keyboard. <br>And sometimes Q and E.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964000/extras/896677d8b534eb9ba01cec763ee9e5e1.poster.avif?t=1772359152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964000/extras/896677d8b534eb9ba01cec763ee9e5e1.webm?t=1772359152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964000/extras/896677d8b534eb9ba01cec763ee9e5e1.mp4?t=1772359152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i>Are you actually reading this?</i></strong><br><br><i>Disclaimer: No human feelings were harmed during the making of this game</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>ABOUT THE ACTUAL GAME</i></h2><br>Escape a chaotic alien planet by fighting through hordes of frenzied monsters - Just kidding, it's a high school game where you play as Mochi, the gossip monger who can't keep her mouth shut. Step into the mind of Mochi and help her focus on her studies. It's your responsibility to control her urge to share every tantalizing piece of gossip to her fellow schoolmates.<br><br><i>\"Gossip is the only thing that spreads faster than wildfire in a dry forest.\" - Our in-house Psychologist</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>WHAT ARE YOU SUPPOSED TO DO?</i></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>As a High school student, all you have to do is focus on your studies.<br></li><li>Attend your daily classes.<br></li><li>Run some errands.<br></li><li>Finish the day without spilling a word, especially to the person the gossip is about.<br></li><li>Things can easily go out of hands if you share it even with a single person.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964000/extras/4cf1cfe0174f4605b10722c89b52c90b.poster.avif?t=1772359152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964000/extras/4cf1cfe0174f4605b10722c89b52c90b.webm?t=1772359152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964000/extras/4cf1cfe0174f4605b10722c89b52c90b.mp4?t=1772359152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>HOW DO YOU PLAY THE GAME?</i></h2><br>All you need is WASD functioning at their best on your keyboard. <br>And sometimes Q and E.",
